<ns144:section xmlns:ns144="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.platforms.jboss.configuration.standardConfigurations.minimal.overview">

  <ns145:title xmlns:ns145="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Overview of the <ns146:emphasis xmlns:ns146="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">minimal</ns146:emphasis> configuration</ns145:title>
  <ns147:para xmlns:ns147="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    The minimal configuration has only the bare minimum required for the JBoss application server
    to be functional. It includes the following standard services:
    <ns148:itemizedlist xmlns:ns148="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      <ns149:listitem xmlns:ns149="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns150:para xmlns:ns150="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">the EJB container, <ns151:emphasis xmlns:ns151="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">JBossServer</ns151:emphasis>,</ns150:para></ns149:listitem>
      <ns152:listitem xmlns:ns152="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns153:para xmlns:ns153="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">the JNDI naming service, and</ns153:para></ns152:listitem>
      <ns154:listitem xmlns:ns154="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns155:para xmlns:ns155="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">the logging service, <ns156:emphasis xmlns:ns156="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Log4J</ns156:emphasis>.</ns155:para></ns154:listitem>
    </ns148:itemizedlist>
  </ns147:para>
</ns144:section>